Source: pfs-hugetlbfs-setup
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: PacketFS <ops@packetfs.local>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://example.com/packetfs
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: pfs-hugetlbfs-setup
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, procps, systemd
Description: Configure hugetlbfs mount for PacketFS
 Installs sysctl defaults and a hugetlbfs mount unit under /mnt/huge1G.
 Falls back to /dev/hugepages on systems without 1GiB hugepages.
